Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 心情也變得超級恬靜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼十分在意的事情嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？阿魯？我既沒有在想阿魯也沒有在意阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}註：日語「有嗎」與「阿魯」發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼都沒在想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級純情少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 送走炎熱的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯漸漸染上了秋天的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是愛麗絲成為正式領航員之後的第一個營業日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 在開始共同練習之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華提議去看看她的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.11,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那份 賞月之夜的心動…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐又很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝您的誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那是嘆息橋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}Ponte dei Sospiri：嘆息橋建於1603年 因橋上死囚的\N嘆息聲而得名 據說戀人們在橋下接吻就可以天長地久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 導遊手冊上寫著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在正在前往的 就是嘆息橋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美得讓人嘆息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 名字的由來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在地球的杜卡雷宮接受了判決的死囚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}杜卡雷宮：古代威尼斯共和國總督的政廳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在經過這座橋的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會深深嘆一口氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然這次來對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 她怎麼這麼緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看起來渾身僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次真的非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們一定還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝二位的惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來客人是很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長 請忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被愛麗絲發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級注意到了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我們偶然路過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 偶然看到了愛麗絲的工作情形…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來二位剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我的工作啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊…妳看 不是還算可以的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 倒划著去追蹤貓咪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還完美地繼承了雅典娜前輩的周到服務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們從那裡就開始看了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷看超級禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…那之外就完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位想說什麼就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像玩具機器人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀僵硬得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是殭屍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有時間讓妳沮喪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為妳已經是正式領航員啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚去賞月如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賞月？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今天天氣不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮一定很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賞月…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 還是第一次賞月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在AQUA沒有這種習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在賞月的時候要有糰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是模仿地球的月亮做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次就吃了兩個 妳好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就吃四個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不輸給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁…禁止吃著碗裡的想著鍋裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩妳超級律人不律己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圓不隆咚的肚子～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞利亞社長圓不隆咚的肚子可不是月見糰子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是郵遞員大叔推薦給我的黑米茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個季節喝熱飲真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 阿魯好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 為什麼阿魯他要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我們三個人賞月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說…說起和星球有關的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就得叫阿魯來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會告訴我們很多事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳…妳那是什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因為上次看流星雨小後輩妳不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才特地叫阿魯過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去接他過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他八成又是在加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能迷路了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華前輩 超級可愛的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳今天邀我賞月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看著月亮 我感覺輕鬆了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 我感覺能像月亮一樣圓滿地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更好地完成自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 再來一杯茶如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？嘛社長不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我加班做得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 工作狂禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀…真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 不過多虧我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能獨佔這深夜的幽靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華小姐 危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧 藍華小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還…還好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼是阿魯你道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我太重了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好城裡的井都是已經廢棄了的枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不至於淹死…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是麻煩了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在還未啟用水道之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個廣場都設置了井口收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用以解決生活用水問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早晚這裡都擠滿了來打水的夫人們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如人們說的 是井邊會議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 嘛社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小後輩帶來這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社長你在聽我說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把·小·後·輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶·過·來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你也跟著跳下來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著 嘛社長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在馬上去把小後輩叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼又跑回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說嘛社長啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的 嘛社長還是貓baby啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 嘛社長是能夠理解人類語言的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色的水星貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會！把小後輩…叫來…的…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之現在我們全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是那樣 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們應不應該抱著期待呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點懸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果變成詭異的賞月了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮為什麼會繞著AQUA轉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為相互吸引的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與相互遠離的力量同時作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我說過的相互吸引的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和圓周運動產生的離心力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成了微妙的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 月亮既無法靠近 也無法遠離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞著AQUA在轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像某人一樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外側的月亮被利用於宇宙空間站等等領域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在真空中完成的科學實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礦物資源的開採
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 妳知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球的月亮上的隕石坑被比喻為各種形狀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如有著巨螯的螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在編織的老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獅子 女性的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿餅的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到兔子我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙空間站的兔子薄餅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說那個很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想吃吃看 前些天就郵購了一些來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說還會附贈讚美月亮的明信片套裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之那種的全部禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井底下還真黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你怕黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力調節員一般都是在黑漆漆的地方工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛在晚上也能看清東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時雖然陽光無法進入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過地下世界的照明設備非常齊全…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯君不用怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 有大姐姐陪著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮變成兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內側的月亮體積大概是外側月亮的1.8倍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在AQUA的靜止軌道內轉動著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8小時以內就能繞著AQUA轉動一周的內側月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是在AQUA上空5900公里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個非常近的軌道內轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個距離跟地球與月球的距離比起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有其65分之1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太過接近的小小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了太多AQUA的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過不久 一定會粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒有距離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到AQUA影響的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只有月亮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但對AQUA來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最最接近不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也被月亮影響著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費掉了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍…藍華小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪費掉什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華 還好找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到妳居然掉到那裡面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是對救命恩人說的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感謝過嘛社長了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 妳們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從「浪費掉了啦」那個時候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 浪費掉什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,產…產生離心力的方法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果害怕靠近而猶豫不前的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子就會餓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是產生引力的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 什麼東西讓人害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿…阿魯的大叔用語讓人害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 什麼東西浪費掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}妳是明知故問對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 雖然這是心血來潮的賞月大會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大家都找回了平時的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就變成了一個非常開心的秋夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里姐姐 月亮除了有引力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許還擁有別的美好的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年秋天我也想參加賞月大會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在激情燃燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像小後輩一樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲很有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 瞬息萬變的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:08.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:18.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:29.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:40.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:52.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:58.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:08.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:13.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:22.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:31.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:36.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:08.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾記得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:18.91,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}湧上心頭的 感動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:29.04,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴著湛藍的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎風前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:40.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我陶醉時 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.89,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我們齊聲歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:52.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:58.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 嶄露頭角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永遠地 充滿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:08.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}讓人陶醉的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:13.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:22.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}每個溫暖的 日子往復著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:31.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不經意間 從那遠方
